article.description: — Jordan Jones and Chris Manon scored 19 points apiece as Cornell narrowly beat Lafayette 90-85 on Friday night.
article.headline: Jones, Manon lead Cornell past Lafayette 90-85
article.linkText: Jones, Manon lead Cornell past Lafayette 90-85
article.story: EASTON, Pa. -- — Jordan Jones and Chris Manon scored 19 points apiece as Cornell narrowly beat Lafayette 90-85 on Friday night. Keller Boothby added 12 points for the Big Red, while Sarju Patel and Greg Dolan each had 10. Manon and Patel each grabbed six rebounds. Tyrone Perry scored a career-high 25 points for the Leopards (0-2). Leo O'Boyle added 19 points.
